<http://www.spektrix.com/capilanouniversity/event/17601ADSBKGQMMPTLRCMTNQVQJNSBPVNG>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Enactus Capilano 10th Year Anniversary Gala";
  schema:description """
	Step into an evening of celebration as Enactus Capilano marks 10 years of impact.​ An Oscars-inspired backdrop, this gala will showcase the projects, people, and partnerships that have shaped our journey while looking ahead to the future we continue to build.​ Guests will enjoy light catering, inspiring stories, and the opportunity to connect with a community driven by purpose and innovation.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Drinks will be available for purchase.​ Tickets are $22, with limited seating available.​ All proceeds go to support future Enactus Capilano activities and projects. ​Join us in celebrating a decade of creating change.​ Dress Code: Formal / Cocktail Attire (Oscars Glam encouraged ✨)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://enactuscapilano.com/\">Enactus Website</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This event takes place at<span><br/></span> <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://penthouseeventsuite.com/home\">The Penthouse Event Suite </a>
""";
