<http://www.spektrix.com/capilanouniversity/event/14601AQGMDCVKHRBCGJLMKRPVNVKVHPJG>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Queer as Funk";
  schema:description """
	<h1>High-energy funk and soul revivalists.</h1><span><br/></span>Bringing fresh takes to beloved funk, soul, and Motown classics, Queer as Funk’s powerful vocals, tight horn arrangements, and irresistible rhythm section make each performance as groovy as it is fun. From Isaac Hayes' “Soul Man” to Bruno Mars’s “Uptown Funk,” the ensemble’s arrangements are creative, their vibe is pure celebration, and their love for each other is palpable, adding depth to the onstage dynamic that models the concept of chosen family.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The group’s individual members are consummate musicians in their own right, having collectively performed with artists like Serena Ryder, Tegan and Sara and Dan Mangan. Queer As Funk has played stages across Canada, including six sold-out headlining shows at Vancouver's legendary Commodore Ballroom—a venue that has hosted icons like Tina Turner and David Bowie. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Performers include: Connie Buna, vocals; Alison Gorman, trumpet; Cat Hiltz, bass; Jocelyn MacDougall, vocals; Allan 'Soulman' Ollivierre, keys; Luis 'Babyface' Melgar, trombone; Marc Van Rosi, guitar; John Nicholson, drums.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5yDK1QW9no8&amp;t=1s\">Watch Video Here</a></h2><span><br/></span><h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Sponsored by Wave 98.3 FM</span></h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">This FREE event takes place at Waterfront Park (200 Esplanade Ave)</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">This concert is part of North Shore Jazz (June 19-28), presented by BlueShore at CapU in partnership with Vancouver International Jazz Festival.</span></span><span><br/></span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-06-28T19:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/capilanouniversity/files/e7f4a15c-eb86-45b3-b838-a37a932be5cf.jpg>;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/capilanouniversity/location/601APNNMRMBJQQPBSCNQGQHGKKCRPSSGN>;
  schema:organizer <https://spektrix.com/capilanouniversity/organization/blueshore-financial-centre-for-the-performing-arts>;
